divs: Sighting DetailsI was looking east last night because the moon was yellowish-orange, then i started lookin west above the treeline towards the city of mounds around 9:30 pm- it was kinda cloudy but the clouds went away and the i noticed 2 red light close together just sittin there in the sky, so i ran inside got the binoculars i watched it for 10 min.. then it took off fast ,BUT WHAT WAS REALLY STRANGE 2 MORE JUST LIKE IT CAME OUT OF NOWHERE AND FOLLOWED IT REALLY FAST!!.it was not loud like a airforce plane- i didnt here any noises at all!!! something is going on in the dark skies and its really got me freaked out!!!!
